You must ensure that anyone who gets a copy of any part of the software from you also gets a copy of these terms.

Commercial Use

Commercial use means using the software for commercial purposes, in commerce, or for commercial advantage, including contributing the software to a product or service that is sold, licensed, or otherwise marketed for commercial use. Commercial use does not include using the software by a person for personal, noncommercial purposes.

